Changes on 2017-04-06:
- Added feature: Can now press 'c' to change color while the clock is running.
- Added feature: Can now press 's' to toggle the seconds field.
- Added feature: Can now press 't' to toggle 12/24 hour time format.
- Update README.md (include new features).

Changes on 2017-04-05:
- Add option to remove the seconds field for 12 and 24 hour time formats.
- Update README.md
    - Add "-s" ("--noseconds") option.

Changes on 2017-04-04:

- Add option to specify 24 hour or 12 hour (default) time format ("-t").
- Specify color with "-c".
- Update Makefile
    - Update install path and some flags.
- Update README.md
    - Add install instructions, usage, examples, and screenshots.
